    "html": "<!DOCTYPE html><html style=\"font-size: 85px;\"><head>\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1\">\n    <meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\">\n    <meta name=\"renderer\" content=\"webkit\">\n    <title>清华大学建筑学院</title>\n    <meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"清华大学建筑学院,建筑学院,世界一流,建筑学,中国特色，城市规划，建筑系\">\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"清华大学是中国著名高等学府，是中国高层次人才培养和科学技术研究的重要基地。清华大学的前身是清华学堂，成立于1911年。截至2017年，清华大学设有20个学院、58个系，已成为一所具有理学、工学、文学、艺术学、历史学、哲学、经济学、管理学、法学、教育学和医学等学科门类的综合性、研究型、开放式大学。截至2017年8月31号，清华大学在学学生总数为47762人，其中本科生15619人、硕士生19062人、博士生13081人。\">\n   \n    <link href=\"/sites/css/font.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n    <link href=\"/sites/css/index.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n    <link href=\"/sites/css/phone.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/sites/js/swiper/swiper-3.4.2.min.css\">\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/sites/js/jquery-3.3.1.min.js\"></script>\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/sites/js/js.js\"></script>\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/sites/js/swiper/swiper-3.4.2.jquery.min.js\"></script>\n</head>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<body>\n<div class=\"headD\"></div>\n   \n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"head\">\n    <div class=\"wal\">\n        <a href=\"\" class=\"logo\"></a>\n        <a href=\"javascript:;\" class=\"navA\"></a>\n        <dl class=\"btn\">\n            <dd><a href=\"/column/INDEX\" class=\"on\">CN</a></dd>\n            <dd><a href=\"/column/Home\">EN</a></dd>\n            \n            \n \n            \n            \n            <dd class=\"search\" value=\"搜索\"> \n              <form name=\"form1\" id=\"search-form-header\" action=\"/column/search\" target=\"_blank\" method=\"post\">\n                   <div class=\"input\">    <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"curpage\" value=\"1\">\n\t               <input name=\"key\" type=\"text\" class=\"inp\" value=\"\" onfocus=\"this.value=''\" onblur=\"if(this.value==''){this.value='';}\">\n                </div>  \n\t         </form>\n        \n           </dd>  \n            <div class=\"submit\">      \n                 <a id=\"searchbtn\" href=\"javascript:;\" onclick=\"$('#search-form-header').submit();\" class=\"btn\" title=\"搜索\">搜索</a>\n           </div> \n      \n            \n        </dl>\n        <div class=\"nav\">\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/INDEX\">首页</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/jj\">简介</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/dt\">动态</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/xs\">系所</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/zs\">招生</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/jx\">教学</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/ky\">科研</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/rw\">人物</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/jl\">交流</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/lj\">链接</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"characterShow_01\">\n    <div class=\"wal\">\n         <div class=\"info\"><a href=\"/column/INDEX\">首页</a><a href=\"/column/rw\"><b>·</b>人物</a>  <a href=\"/column/sz\"><b>·</b>师资</a>  <a href=\"/column/rw_jzhj\"><b>·</b>建筑技术科学系</a>  </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"name\">曹彬</div>\n        <div class=\"msg\">\n            电话： <br>\n            传真： <br>\n            E-mail：caobin@tsinghua.edu.cn\n        </div>\n    \n       <div class=\"img\"><img src=\"/upload_files/image/1644404081948_6D.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n   \n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"wal characterShow\">\n   \n     <div class=\"content\"><p><br></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体,SimSun; font-size: 12px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:10px;line-height:27px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:黑体\">研究和教学方向</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">人体热舒适与健康</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">室内环境品质</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">绿色建筑技术</span></p><p style=\"line-height:27px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:黑体\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:10px;line-height:27px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:黑体\">教育简历</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\">2007- 2012<span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">清华大学建筑学院土木工程（暖通空调）专业，获工学博士学位</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\">2003- 2007<span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">清华大学建筑学院建筑环境与设备工程专业，获工学学士学位</span></p><p style=\"line-height:27px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:黑体\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:10px;line-height:27px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:黑体\">工作履历</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\">2019</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">至今</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\"> <span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">清华大学建筑学院</span> <span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">特别研究员、博士生导师</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\">2017- 2019<span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">清华大学建筑学院</span> <span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">博士生导师</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\">2016- 2017<span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">清华大学建筑学院</span> <span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">助理研究员</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\">2015- 2016<span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">美国哈佛大学绿色建筑与城市研究中心</span> <span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">博士后</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\">2012- 2014<span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">清华大学建筑学院</span> <span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">博士后</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:10px;line-height:27px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:黑体\">主要学术兼职</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">国际室内空气学会</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\"> <span>(ISIAQ) <span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">热舒适分会秘书</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">国际能源署</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\"> (IEA) </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">建筑与社区节能</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\">Annex69</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">项目</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\"> <span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">秘书长</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">教育部高等学校建筑环境与能源应用工程专业教学指导分委员会</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\"> <span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">秘书</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">中国建筑学会建筑物理分会 理事</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">中国城市科学研究会绿色建筑与节能专业委员会</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\"><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">委员兼青委会副秘书长</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">中国环境科学学会室内环境与健康分会</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\"> <span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">青委会主任委员</span></p><p style=\"line-height:27px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:黑体\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:10px;line-height:27px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:黑体\">课程教学</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">专业基础课：建筑环境学（</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">学分，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\">48</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">学时，合讲）</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">专业限选课：人体热舒适（</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">学分，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\">32</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">学时，主持）</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">全校通识课：室内环境与健康（</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">学分，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\">32</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">学时，主持）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:27px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:黑体\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:10px;line-height:27px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:黑体\">荣誉与获奖</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">教育部国家级人才奖励计划青年学者，2020</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">国家科技进步二等奖（5/10），2019</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">北京市科技新星，2019</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">国际室内空气学会</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:black\"> (ISIAQ) </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">“雅格鲁杰出青年科学家奖</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:black\"> (Yaglou Award)</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">”，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:black\">2020</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">美国暖通空调学会</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:black\"> (ASHRAE) </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">“拉尔夫</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:Wingdings;color:black\"><span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">内文斯生理与人类环境奖</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:black\"> <span>(Ralph G. Nevins Physiology and Human Environment Award)</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">”，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:black\">2019</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">中国城市科学研究会绿色建筑与节能专业委员会青年委员突出贡献奖，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:black\">2018</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">全国建筑环境与能源应用工程专业青年教师讲课技能竞赛特等奖，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:black\">2019</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">清华大学教师“林枫辅导员奖”，</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:black\">2020</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">清华大学优秀班主任一等奖，</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:black\">2020</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">清华大学疫情防控期间在线教学优秀奖，2020</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">大学生研究训练（SRT）计划优秀指导教师，2021</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">清华大学就业工作先进个人，2020</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">清华大学招生工作10年年功奖，2021</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">清华大学优秀招生教师，2017</span></p><p style=\"line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:10px;line-height:27px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:黑体\">近期主要科研项目</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">国家自然科学基金面上项目“人体热舒适的部位需求分布特征与局部冷热调节模式研究”，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\">2021- 2024</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">，主持</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">国家自然科学基金面上项目“建筑环境儿童热舒适机理与评价模型研究”，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:black\">2018- 2021</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">，主持</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">国家自然科学基金青年项目“人体局部接触式热暴露对热舒适的影响研究”，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:black\">2016- 2018</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">，主持</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">国家自然科学基金重点项目“未来城市建筑室内环境营造理论和设计方法”，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:black\">2019- 2023</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">，子课题负责人</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">国家十三五重点研发计划科技冬奥重点专项课题“赛道环境营造及观赛环境保障技术研究”，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:black\">2018- 2021</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">，主持</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">国家十三五重点研发计划课题“绿色建筑实际性能与设计预期差异机理研究”，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:black\">2016- 2020</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">，子课题负责人</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">国家十二五科技支撑计划课题“天津生态城绿色建筑规划设计关键技术集成与示范”，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:black\">2013- 2017</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">，子课题负责人</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">北京市自然科学基金项目“京津冀地区办公建筑基于能耗控制需求的适应性热舒适评价方法研究”，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:black\">2015- 2016</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\">，主持</span></p><p style=\"line-height:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:10px;line-height:27px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:黑体\">代表性论文</span></strong></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:56px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:Wingdings;color:red\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:56px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:Wingdings\"><span><span style=\"font:9px 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\">Yeyu Wu, </span><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\">Bin Cao*</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\">. (2022). Recognition and prediction of individual thermal comfort requirement based on local skin temperature. <em>Journal of Building Engineering</em>, 49: 104025.</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:56px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:Wingdings\"><span><span style=\"font:9px 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif\">Xinyu Jia, <strong>Bin Cao*</strong>, Yingxin Zhu. (2022). A climate chamber study on subjective and physiological responses of airport passengers from walking to a sedentary status in summer. Bu